\begin_layout Section
Writing style
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A thesis document is comparable to a research report or scientific book,
 like Tanenbaum's 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Computer Networks
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
 Scientific writing has to be a formal document - much more formal than
 many articles in the Internet.
 Colloquial and informal writing is undesirable.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Formal and informal English differ in word choice, word usage, and grammatical
 structures.
 Informal writing might utilize the words 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

kid
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

how come
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

