\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 as a noun.
 A formal writer might prefer 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

child
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

why
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

quotation
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
